; Greenheart Glade — Ranger intro arena.
; A clearing in the deep wood. Moss-soft floor, ringed by tall conifer trunks.
; Tree stumps scattered as cover (the Glade Terror's roar pushes you off them).
; Mid-day light filtered green through the canopy. Birds went silent the
; moment you stepped in. You are not the only hunter here.

